name: Jane Smith
summary: Technology leader with 20+ years of experience in software development, cloud computing, and AI-driven innovations. Proven expertise in scaling engineering teams and driving digital transformation.

skills.specialized skill: Software Development, Cloud Computing & SaaS, AI & Machine Learning, Digital Transformation

experience.description: Built a scalable cloud-based SaaS platform, increasing revenue by 200%. Led a team of 200+ engineers across multiple global locations. Championed AI adoption, enhancing product efficiency by 50%.
Managed a $100M R&D budget, accelerating product innovation. Transitioned the company from monolithic architecture to microservices.
